      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1454710"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/pansin/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1013920-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/pansin/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">pansin</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-07-29"
      class="main-meta">2008-07-29 09:22:37</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1454710_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  高情商是每个人渴望但未必拥有的，那么，是什么原因呢？  《社交商》不是一本东拼西凑，闭门造车充满臆想的社交指南。也别期望读过之后个人的社交技巧和个人情商能达到飞跃。这本书值得观看是因为里面介绍的是神经心理学对人的大脑的解读，追本溯源，了解情商和社交商差异产生...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1454710_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1454710_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



